# Weavox — Dual Licensing

This software is released under a dual-license model.

---

## License Options

### 1. Open Source (GPL v3)

For open-source projects, community contributors, and non-commercial use:

- **License File:** [LICENSE-GPL.txt](./LICENSE-GPL.txt)
- **Conditions:** You must disclose source code of any derivative works under the same GPL v3 license.

### 2. Commercial License

For companies and individuals who want to use Weavox in proprietary, closed-source products:

- **License File:** [LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md](./LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md)
- **Contact:** licensing@skylinetechone.com
- **Website:** weavox.app

---

## Which License Do You Need?

| Use Case | Recommended License |
|---------|----------------|
| Open-source project | GPL v3 |
| Personal/non-commercial | GPL v3 |
| Internal business tool | Commercial (Starter) |
| SaaS platform | Commercial (Growth/Business) |
| Enterprise solution | Commercial (Enterprise) |
| Mobile app resale | Commercial (Business+) |

---

## Quick Comparison

| Aspect | GPL v3 | Commercial |
|--------|--------|-----------|
| Source code disclosure | Required | Not required |
| Attribution | Required | Varies by tier |
| Closed-source products | Not permitted | Permitted |
| Build competing apps | Not permitted | 24-month restriction |
| Resale as standalone | Not permitted | Not permitted |
| Commercial SaaS | Not permitted | Permitted |

---

## Obtaining a Commercial License

To purchase a commercial license:

1. **Email:** licensing@skylinetechone.com
2. **Website:** weavox.app/commercial
3. **Tiers:** Starter ($2,400/yr), Growth ($12,000/yr), Business ($60,000/yr), Enterprise (custom)

Include in your inquiry:
- Company name and location
- Intended use case
- Estimated monthly active users (MAU)
- Required deployment count

